snippet.title: Helldivers 2 - "The Fight for Freedom Begins " Launch Trailer | PS5 & PC Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-gb/games/helldivers-2/   https://store.steampowered.com/agecheck/app/553850/

Do you read me? They’re… everywhere.
Bugs. Bots. Killers that need to be stopped.
Join an elite online squad and unload epic firepower and strategies in the name of democracy.
Enlist in the galaxy’s last line of offence on PS5 or PC and stand by for orders.
Out 8 February.

#ps5 #ps5games #pcgames #helldivers #helldivers2 

Rated Mature
